            <updated>2020-07-24T16:24:03.000Z</updated>
            <author><name>Max Roser</name></author>
            <summary><![CDATA[For most of our history we were losing terribly against the microbes. Only recently did we turn the battle in our favour. Vaccines were a major breakthrough, as the data shows. Now in the fight against the coronavirus too, our biggest hope is to find an effective vaccine.<br><br><a href="https://ourworldindata.org/microbes-battle-science-vaccines" target="_blank"><img src="https://ourworldindata.org/app/uploads/2020/07/vaccines-768x598.png"/></a>]]></summary>
